snippet: Guangzhou R&F scored a 3-1 win over the Central Coast Mariners of Australia to join Gamba Osaka of Japan, Seongnam of South Korea and Buriram United of Thailand in Group F.
abstract: Chinese soccer club Guangzho R&F beats Central Coast Mariners of Australia, 3-1, to earn spot in the Asian Champions League.
lead_paragraph: Guangzhou R&F scored a 3-1 win over the Central Coast Mariners of Australia to join Gamba Osaka of Japan, Seongnam of South Korea and Buriram United of Thailand in Group F.

headline.main: Chinese Team Earns Spot in Asian Champions League
